comment:
Ok I just have to get this off my chest. It truly bothers me how much fame she is getting from all of this. Before she was with Johnny Depp and before these lawsuits, not a whole lot of people knew who she was and she‚Äôd only done small roles or smaller movies ever since all of this, now everyone knows who she is. Her career is seeming to take off while his name is being dragged through the mud and he‚Äôs basically being blacklisted. How is that fair? There‚Äôs evidence against her too. She should‚Äôve been fired from Aquaman 2 and definitely not receiving new roles. But because Hollywood doesn‚Äôt want to seem sexist against women or ok with abusers, she gets everything while Johnny Depp watches his career be taken away from him. 

Plus how she smirks all the time and her overall demeanor just doesn‚Äôt say abuse victim to me. I‚Äôve dealt with abuse victims as a nurse and this is not how they act....at all. She is not an innocent victim, there is a lot of evidence making it pretty clear she was an abuser. I don‚Äôt think Johnny Depp did everything right or didn‚Äôt have some culpability but she is not the victim she wants everyone to believe. It truly angers me that she is acting this way because this could lead future TRUE abuse victims not being taken seriously. She‚Äôs defamating an entire group of people essentially. I just hope someday the truth comes to light and people stop giving her everything she asks for.
